    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >由骰子引领，被卡牌掌控。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/c81795f1614e2a4748094aac904e5383.poster.avif?t=1771392601\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/c81795f1614e2a4748094aac904e5383.webm?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/c81795f1614e2a4748094aac904e5383.mp4?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●《Culdcept》是什么？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款在格子上前进、争夺领地的卡牌构筑类策略游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵活运用召唤与魔法，迈向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系列首作《Culdcept®》发售至今已有近30年，而《Culdcept BEGINS》正是该系列的最新作品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●故事</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事发生在众神创造的巴布拉什卡大陆上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王立学府召唤师学院位于大陆中央，长年致力于培养召唤师，助其更好地操控&lt;卡尔多&gt;石板之力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >转入召唤师学院的卡穆尔，其能力受到认可，被选入王国近卫召唤师联队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●游戏系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投掷骰子前进，驱使卡牌战斗—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个桌游中，运气与策略决定了胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既能体验到系列作品原汁原味的魅力，又能享受到经过打磨而进化，愈发容易上手的游戏玩法。​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/ea0f44c17edfac3b192770b525293559.poster.avif?t=1771392601\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/ea0f44c17edfac3b192770b525293559.webm?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/ea0f44c17edfac3b192770b525293559.mp4?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>●卡牌</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过400种卡面，全部焕然一新。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情搭配种类丰富的卡牌，运用您的策略获得胜利吧。​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>・生物卡</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以召唤生物的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以用来增加自己的领地，或是夺取敌人的领地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >共有5个属性，各个生物卡的能力各异。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>・物品卡</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物品卡是战斗时为生物提供帮助的卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了强化生物的攻击和防御以外，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分物品卡还拥有特殊能力，甚至能帮你在不利局面下找到胜机！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>・咒语卡</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用咒语卡可以为自己创造节奏，有时还能将对手逼入绝境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果用得巧妙，还能直接左右对局胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想获得胜利，咒语卡不可或缺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/73dbd552d54fa6ec09d23a61f432eea8.poster.avif?t=1771392601\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/73dbd552d54fa6ec09d23a61f432eea8.webm?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322630/extras/73dbd552d54fa6ec09d23a61f432eea8.mp4?t=1771392601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
